Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最討厭和最喜歡產生的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是兩個人的推理與懸疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.20,0:00:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謎樣的中式旋轉餐桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.10,0:00:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭的回憶因此復甦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一行人拿著小蘭抽獎得到的餐券
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到橫濱的中華街用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡認識了電影工作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.70,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電影導演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.00,0:01:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磯上海藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電影導演助理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊東基傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.90,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦京吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製作人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.80,0:02:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端四朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.40,0:02:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並和他們一起用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端竟然死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端的座位上沒有檢驗出毒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他使用過的盤子和濕毛巾上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻發現了毒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.60,0:02:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在死者旁邊的毛利叔叔成了下毒的嫌疑人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈哈哈哈 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是第一次來這家餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是初次見到川端先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼非殺他不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你女兒第一次來這個飯店就被星探看中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那麼好的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.60,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的只是偶爾來到這個餐廳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉色不太好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是站得有點久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就過來坐一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想叔叔很快就會破案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 小蘭氣色十分不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不快點帶她去醫院的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.90,0:03:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中華街 雨中的似曾相識（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人調換有毒的濕毛巾是在換座位之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:04:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時坐在死者右邊的你最可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小蘭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.10,0:04:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在廁所裡發現了裝毒物的容器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.10,0:04:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.10,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去廁所的時候把毛巾拿過去下毒的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不是我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.10,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣犯人就絕對不是小五郎叔叔了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為叔叔來了這個飯店就沒去過廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且川端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是擦了弄灑的湯以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿著濕毛巾就換了座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得誰都沒辦法調換濕毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還是有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不讓別人發現的換毛巾的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是利用了這個旋轉餐桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把下了毒的濕毛巾放在轉盤的旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果轉得正好的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濕毛巾就正好掉在了川端的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼如何啊 你這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個突然掉下來誰都會覺得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是恰巧沒被發現的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.70,0:05:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果用能夠使毛巾掉下來的速度轉桌子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盤子跟碗之類的也都會掉下來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.60,0:05:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊就是自己的毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會用那個毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得在我拿醬油和辣油的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好幾次把桌子轉過來馬上又轉了回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.70,0:06:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得那時桌上料理的排列順序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按順時針是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回鍋肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.00,0:06:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青椒肉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹黃炒蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糖醋裡脊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後是蒸籠蓋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醬油在糖醋裡脊和皮蛋的中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣油在回鍋肉和蒸籠蓋子的中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的座位順序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從被殺的川端順時針下去依次是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.50,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.40,0:06:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.30,0:06:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.10,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後醬油總是回到叔叔的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣油總是在北浦的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端說過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我對蛋過敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看到有蛋的菜就覺得噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看到就覺得噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那邊請注意一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.90,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 鑑識員叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有問題想請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼啊 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們既然檢驗了菜裡有沒有毒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼旋轉餐桌也有檢驗了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.10,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些地方也檢驗了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快點去檢驗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎叔叔是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.50,0:07:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個沉睡的小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.30,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個有毒的濕毛巾上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有沾上什麼奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒物以外嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡茶色的污漬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.80,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聞起來那像是湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小弟弟你看到的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端把湯弄在褲子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後用濕毛巾擦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個時候沾上的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.20,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有沾上其他東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沾上別的什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去告訴小五郎叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.30,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端不是被掉包了的濕毛巾毒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在他死了之後再調換的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人調換的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據應該還在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個桌子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在廁所裡在自己的濕毛巾下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在用餐中把自己的毛巾和死者的調包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.10,0:09:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在死者兩邊坐著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 小蘭和柯南 沒注意的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不明白啊 到底是怎麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三位嫌疑人都是電影製作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不是用看不見的繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把有毒的濕毛巾吊起來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.80,0:09:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈…哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的冷氣太冷了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽哥哥說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎一開始都說一些看起來很沒用的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是假裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.00,0:09:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一陣奇怪的聲音和舞蹈後 態度完全改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像突然換了一個人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是哥哥說得誇張了點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道那個奇妙的舞蹈就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜疑就到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家能不能都坐回到座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.50,0:10:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案發時和被害人一起坐在桌子上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊東 磯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.50,0:10:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有北浦三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.60,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 讓我來仔細和你們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯的時候所發生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡的小五郎的推理秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.80,0:10:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者的座位上由橫溝警官來代替吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從右邊開始案發時順次是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.90,0:10:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.70,0:11:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭的座位上請別的警員代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.10,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒身體不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭和死者中間位置上的柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.10,0:11:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.10,0:11:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始說明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.20,0:11:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案發前發生的不可思議的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桌子的轉盤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人轉那個轉盤欺負我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.90,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎叔叔面前的轉盤上有醬油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把那個轉到面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.50,0:12:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上又會轉回到小五郎叔叔面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.70,0:12:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後想要拿北浦先生面前的辣油也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子轉到附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又會馬上轉回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.70,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是誰在欺負我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.10,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼說的和案件有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.10,0:12:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.30,0:12:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下兇手會自己露出狐狸尾巴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎叔叔這麼說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手自己？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包子來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 怎麼在這種時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在審查中途的時候給這個孩子一個包子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利偵探是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.90,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.20,0:13:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好好想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是剛發生過殺人案的桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道哪裡沾了毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓剛碰過桌子的孩子吃東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑑識員剛檢查過這個桌子 哪裡都沒有發現…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 正如磯上所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還殘留著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.10,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們看不到的角落裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.00,0:13:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快給我說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒下在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個旋轉餐桌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手放在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如果像這個蟹黃炒蛋和皮蛋的盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.90,0:14:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠的很近 又都伸出來一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那…那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能像這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用手指夾住桌子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.30,0:14:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個轉盤的下面下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要讓被害者碰這裡也很難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這兩樣菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是被殺的川端討厭的東西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.50,0:14:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是看到就覺得討厭的食物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端對蛋過敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請橫溝警官確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者所坐的 也就是你的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放著這兩盤菜的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣油在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得小鬼在轉動轉盤的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人才會又把它轉回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端為了避開那兩個菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沾上了毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣好幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.10,0:15:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣油是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候醬油在小鬼面前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在拿醬油的時候也會轉回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓他沾到毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡就一定要沾上毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下毒必須要在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接用手拿的北京烤鴨上來前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會被誰碰到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說小鬼在拿醬油的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.70,0:15:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人還沒有下毒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.30,0:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.60,0:16:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是兇手看到了北京烤鴨上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.40,0:16:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才要在兩個盤子間的轉盤下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為柯南轉動轉盤 沒有下成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就轉回來好幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醬油在你面前的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩盤菜面前的人就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.50,0:16:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這個人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚在這裡殺害了川端的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.00,0:16:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個沾有大量毒物的濕毛巾是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個本來是磯上的毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.70,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在廁所下了毒以後回到座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那兩個盤子之間的轉盤上下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在川端倒下的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁亂把川端的濕毛巾調包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓人發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的濕毛巾上也沾上了湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是想把自己的濕毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得和死者擦過褲子的濕毛巾一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只漏掉了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端的褲子是牛仔褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.10,0:17:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你調包的川端的濕毛巾上沾有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和湯一起沾上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.10,0:17:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲的藍色污漬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.60,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個濕毛巾在磯上面前就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.20,0:17:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磯上是兇手的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.00,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個毛巾還不能說是鐵證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了嫁禍磯上而放在那裡也是可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.60,0:18:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是磯上的話會自己坦白的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才柯南摸了沾有毒的轉盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要用手吃包子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而被你制止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這說明你還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.30,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端要是對理香也有點良心的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.80,0:18:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.30,0:18:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理香是一年前死的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是拍攝事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不是事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那完全是謀殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來演到最後那個鏡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理香應該換成了替身演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.80,0:19:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端本來就知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.10,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.20,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說理香跟她說想自己演最後一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果後果慘重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也只是笑過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喊停的機會要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說她是個新手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她當傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導演也是人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直看著攝影機鏡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就被她迷住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.10,0:20:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管她有多麼大的缺點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不明白這一點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一輩子也就這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回局裡說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然你應該已經把毒藥擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.30,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我對那個小孩坐視不管怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.90,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像川端那種沒血沒淚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會改變詢問的措辭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你無話可說的尖銳措辭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.20,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是上帝給了我良心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.00,0:21:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的不錯喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為導演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於你那個魔鬼一樣的問訊 我深感敬佩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.00,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我本來就是不信上帝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.10,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上真的有上帝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.50,0:21:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個冷靜的女人的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.20,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.80,0:21:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.20,0:21:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.50,0:21:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了天就該放晴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.90,0:21:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.40,0:21:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像能聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.30,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上真的有上帝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.50,0:21:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 天使從來沒有對我微笑過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次也沒有呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.90,0:22:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.80,0:22:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.40,0:22:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.30,0:22:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.00,0:22:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一也在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.10,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.30,0:22:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作起來 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.90,0:23:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.50,0:23:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭…小蘭姐姐她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.70,0:23:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燒得那麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.00,0:23:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.50,0:23:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.60,0:23:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.10,0:24:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.20,0:24:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.40,0:24:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.60,0:24:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.40,0:24:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新一嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.70,0:24:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.10,0:24:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一NY事件（事件篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.90,0:24:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.30,0:24:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞臺服裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.60,0:24:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集的舞臺是回憶中的紐約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.80,0:24:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點讓人懷念的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.93,0:00:18.27,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.43,0:00:28.03,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們兩人所訴說的未來裡 就像有你在身邊的棲身地一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.57,0:00:31.66,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.82,0:00:35.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,把我當作是你的全部喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.03,0:00:43.59,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,相信兩個人牽著的手 發誓我們一起走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.66,0:00:50.39,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,“最討厭” 即使是謊言我也說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.42,0:00:57.44,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,“最喜歡” 如果是謊言我就不會說喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.18,0:01:05.61,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無法見面的時候 你就像無暇考慮其他東西一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的心裡只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.98,0:01:15.37,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.53,0:01:24.88,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓兩個愛永不分離 請緊緊擁抱對方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.75,0:01:32.06,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此不安的夜晚 還是會來臨的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.09,0:01:40.14,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,840)}那時候 要緊緊地擁抱我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.87,0:22:27.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,每個清晨來臨的時候都會想起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.21,0:22:33.98,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只要在你身旁就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.51,0:22:40.61,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕因時間的流逝而哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.85,0:22:45.84,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在漸漸改變的人的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.53,0:22:59.42,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有期望也就不會失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.25,0:23:06.22,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,然而不能沒有追求啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.50,0:23:13.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無論前方的道路是何等艱辛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.47,0:23:20.65,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在夢醒以後 你還是那麼遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.93,0:23:26.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是自作多情的徒勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.44,0:23:33.79,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,花雨中的道路還是沒有絲毫改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.07,0:23:40.83,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,880)}真想挽著你的手漫步其中啊
